Master’s degree or above in Economics;
At least 3 years of experience in economic research, preferably in the banking sector;
Excellent analytical and presentation skills;
A critical thinker willing to challenge mainstream views;
Good command of English, Chinese and Mandarin.

 (Candidate with more experience will be considered as Senior Economist)

