Assist to formulate and implement personal customer segment strategies to achieve the business targets and improve customer experience. Design and monitor the implementation of segment business plans through initiatives / activities on acquisition, cross-selling, service upgrade, customer loyalty and retention, etc. Work with various internal and external stakeholders to meet customers’ needs from a holistic perspective. Design appropriate sales tools to facilitate frontline to achieve the planned business targets and objectives. Collect and analyze data and feedbacks from time to time and make business recommendations for continuous improvement.


Requirements:

Degree or above with major in Business Administration, Marketing, Finance or related discipline;
At least 4 years working experience in banking industry; solid experience in customer management, marketing, or product management is preferred;
Familiar with banking products and operations / service enhancement is an advantage;
A good team player with strong business acumen and analytical skills;
Excellent communications and presentation skills;
Proficient in both spoken and written English and Chinese, fluent in Putonghua is preferable.

